===Noun===
'''handbag''' (''plural'' '''handbags''')

#(''especially British'') A small bag used by women (or sometimes by men) for carrying various small personal items.

===Verb===
'''to handbag'''
# To be a assaulted by a woman, particulaly used to describe the agressive stance of the ex-British Prime minister Margaret Thatcher

